N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 53.1 - Registration statement form

State Regulations

The ticket distributor registration statement required under section 23.23 of
article 23 of the Arts and Cultural Affairs Law shall be designated form TD-1A and shall be filed with the Bureau of Securities of the Department of

Law at 28 Liberty Street, New York, NY 10005 during normal business days of the Department of Law between the hours of 9 a.m. and 5
p.m. Notes
